column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SPLASH GUM STRAWBERRY AND LIME, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050074983
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (maltitols, sorbitols, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, humectant (glycerol), flavourings, gelatine (bovine), acids (malic acid, citric acid), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), colours (E171, E100, E141), glazing agent (carnauba wax), thickener (E466). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
